data.name: label22.Text
data.value:
Hey there! Thank you for checking out WCT. This tool was made by a small developer and content creator called @oliverstechcorner (aka @oliverstech). If you do like my work, any feedback would be loved! This tool is made open-source to allow everyone to learn and develop their own programs with the help of my (probs not the best thought out) code!
Any submissions and reports are highly appreciated, and will only help to make this project grow bigger and even better than it currently is.
Having said this, by no means should you have paid for this against your will. Donations are completely voluntary and are not required to use this utility.
